AssignmentSeven Start Name Developed By: Liam Clow & Joshua Boag ScoreActivity This is a simple ball throwing game. Throw your yellow ball from the left-hand side of the screen toward the blue targets. Accuracy and ball Speed award more points when the target is struck! Watch out for moving obstacles, portals and red boosters. All of these objects can be used to aid you in getting the winning throw!>
